        "106位",
        "112-127位"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，Acknowledgment Number的拼写检查一下，应该是Acknowledgment而不是Acknowlegment，少了一个d。还有确认号字段是64-95位，这个范围没错吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Acknowledgment Number",
        "64-95"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "感谢指出，Acknowledgment确实拼错了，已修正为Acknowledgment Number，64-95位的范围是正确的。现在所有字段都准确了：Source Port、Destination Port、Sequence Number、Acknowledgment Number、Data Offset、Reserved、六个控制位、Window、Checksum、Urgent Pointer，以及带Education_StudentDB标注的Options和Data。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Acknowledgment Number",
